    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1888-11-26T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1888-11-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="317" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d317">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">de Claparède</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1888-11-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 26,
                                    1888</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I received yesterday at my residence, with
                            the sincerest concern and distress, the melancholy announcement of the
                            serious amputation to which President Hertenstein had been
                            subjected.</p>
                <p>The President of the United States instructs me to convey an expression
                            of his sympathy, and his hopes that President Hertenstein is rapidly
                            recuperating from the operation, which he trusts may restore him to his
                            usual health.</p>
                <p>Accept, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">T. F. Bayard.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
